Vitality Enhancement|Helldivers resist injury with this one.
UAV Recon Booster|The range of the radar increases.
Stamina Enhancement|Stamina capacity and recovery is increased.
Muscle Enhancement|Make your way across and up difficult terrain with this booster.
Increased Reinforcement Budget|The number of reinforcements is increased.
